name: Flaccid Horse Penis - Concept LoRA
description:
Please, check the description, there is plenty of useful information.

Erect Horse Penis LoRA - Erect version of horse penis LoRA

As you can see, now it's separated concepts, flaccid, erect, etc.

What different from another horse penis LoRAs?

It's different from those i've tested.

  1. Change's style of your basic model just a little bit. (will be improved for flaccid)

  2. Compatibility. Works pretty well with different LoRAs, like characters or even style.

  3. Diversity in sizes, ability to control.

Indroduction:

Flaccid horse penis LoRA. Works pretty good with other LoRAs and humanoid characters.

Model used for previews: DivineEleganceMix V5

Recommendations:

  • 1.0 weight for most models

  • See relevant tag tips

Relevant genital tag tips:

You can adjust tag weight by placing it in brackets and specify value: (Flaccid:1.4), where 1.4 is a modifier. Base tag weight is 1.0 on being put to your prompt box..

So, Large Flaccid Penis and (Large Flaccid Penis:1.4) would produce different sized schlongs. The second one also can be much bigger or equal to Huge Penis.

You can combine tags below as you like to get the result you need.

Smallest possible penis - Big, the stallionis maximus - Gigantic

  • Eqcok as an activation tags

  • Flaccid | Size Flaccid Penis (only v1) | Size Penis for penis state and size

    • Size value can be Big | Large | Huge or Gigantic

    • You can use both size tags at once to achieve “middle” result

  • Size Testicles for testicles size

    • Size value can be Big | Large | Huge or Gigantic

    • You can use two tags at once to achieve “middle” or even bigger result

  • Sagging | Resting Testicles for testicles state

    • Sagging for saggy testicles

    • Resting for on-surface state (like breast rest)

  • Cock Sheath for proper penis sheath

Example penis prompts:

For large flaccid penis:

  • eqcok, erection, (large flaccid penis, large penis, large testicles:1.2), cock sheath

If you want make less messy/dripping/wet penises, just type:

  • (Precum, Cum, Wet, Suggestive Fluid:1.2) in your negative prompt

Credits:

Trained on NAI Anime Full.

Dataset of 60 pictures (v1), 5 repeats, 10 epochs, Clip Skip - 2

Dataset of 130 pictures (v2), 3 repeats, 10 epochs, Clip Skip - 2

Really big thanks to:

  • Some good folks from Discord server

  • You, for reading, downloading and reviewing this LoRA

  • Less style impact, need more work on it still, 150 or 200 pics in general

  • More male characters in dataset who wanted it in earlier versions of LoRA

  • Improved from below and from above views

  • Way less problems with sitting or lying characters

  • Removed size flaccid penis tags from dataset, now uses justsize penis

  • Because of large anthro characters in dataset, better anthros

I hope you'll have a good experience using newer version of Flaccid Horse Penis LoRA.
